Backport to fix memory leak in C2 parsing; applies cleanly; All tests passed; Risk is low: there is no follow-up bug since mainline integration almost an year ago. The code change is to use temp Arena instead of `node_arena` for allocating `GrowableArray` in `Parse::catch_call_exceptions` and switch to using stack memory for `GrowableArrays`.</comment>
